h1. configure-for-job-only

h2. Usage
{code}
grails configure-for-job-only [job name]
{code}

h2. Description

Configures an application / plugin as a job only project.  Grails creates a lot of folders and files by default, a lot
of which are unnecessary when you only need to create jobs.  If a job name is not provided the user will be prompted to
add one.